investments.description: Mwayi wosiyanasiyana wachuma ndi kusanthula kwaukadaulo, zida zoona chiopsezo, ndi kutsata momwe zikuyendera pa mitundu yambiri ya chuma.

plans.description: Njira zosankhidwa za nkhani zachuma ndi mbiri zatsatanetsatane za chiopsezo, deta ya momwe zinachitira m'mbuyomu, ndi mawu osinthika kuti agwirizane ndi zolinga zanu zandalama.
plans.title: Mapulani Obweretsera

staking.title: Mphotho za Staking
staking.description: Pezani ndalama zopanda kugwira ntchito kudzera mu staking ya cryptocurrency ndi mitengo yopikisana ya APY, nthawi zosinthika zotsekera, ndi kugawa kwamphotho kokhazikika.

ico.description: Kulowa koyambirira ku Initial Coin Offerings zodziwika bwino ndi malipoti ofufuza mwatsatanetsatane, kusanthula kwa tokenomics, ndi kutsata nkhani zachuma.
ico.title: Kugulitsa Matokeni

marketplace.title: Msika
marketplace.description: Fufuzani misika yapamwamba ya digito ndi yakuthupi ndi malonda otetezedwa, ogulitsa ovomerezeka, ndi chitetezo chokwanira cha ogula.

nft.description: Pezani, pangani, ndi kugulitsa chuma chapadera cha digito m'msika wathu wa NFT wosankhidwa ndi kuthekera kwa auction ndi ndalama za olemba.
nft.title: Msika wa NFT

store.title: Sitolo
store.description: Msika wapamwamba wokhala ndi zinthu za digito ndi zakuthupi ndi kukonza malipiro otetezedwa, kutumiza padziko lonse, ndi chitetezo cha ogula.

services.title: Ntchito
services.description: Ntchito zaukadaulo ndi zida zopititsa patsogolo lanu logulitsa, kuphatikizapo mapulogalamu a affiliate, zinthu zophunzitsira, ndi chithandizo chapamwamba.

affiliate.description: Pezani ndalama kuchokera ku network yanu kudzera mu pulogalamu yathu yokwanira ya affiliate ndi commissions yopikisana, kutsata kwa nthawi yeniyeni, ndi zida zotsatsira.
affiliate.title: Pulogalamu ya Affiliate

support.title: Malo Othandizira
support.description: Chithandizo chaukadaulo cha makasitomala ndi kuyang'anira ma ticket, kuthekera kwa live chat, ndi kuyang'anira ma account odzipatulira kwa ogwiritsa ntchito apamwamba.

faq.description: Zolemba zokwanira, maphunziro, ndi mafunso omwe amafunsidwa pafupipafupi kuti akuthandizeni kugwiritsa ntchito kuthekera kwa nsanja.
faq.title: Malo a Chidziwitso

merchant.title: Chipata cha Malonda
merchant.description: Landirani malipiro kuchokera kwa makasitomala kudzera pa chipata chathu chotetezeka cha malipiro ndi kulumikizana kwa API ndi kutsatira zogulitsa nthawi yeniyeni.

insights.title: Zidziwitso
insights.description: Kusanthula kwamsika kwaluso, zidziwitso zamalonda, ndi nkhani zamakampani kuchokera kwa gulu lathu la akatswiri azachuma ndi ofufuza amsika.
